'''Bantha Breakfast Biscuits''' were a popular food of the [[Biscuit Baron]] chain. They were often eaten with [[blue sauce]]. The biscuits were also noted to be the source of the [[Giant Amorphous Bantha Breakfast Biscuit]], which were created by the accidental mixing of preservatives in the biscuits with [[Bantha/Legends|bantha]] genetic material.

[[Jedi Order/Legends|Jedi]] [[Padawan/Legends|Padawan]] [[Halagad Ventor]] ate a bantha breakfast biscuit before his [[Battle of Skye|mission]] to the planet [[Skye/Legends|Skye]] and immetiately regurgitated it after his [[Escape pod/Legends|escape pod]] crashed on the planet.

